reviewText: Ken Davis has a unique method of sharing God's truth.  People will enjoy and also come away with a message for their souls.
On time, good condition. Enjoyed this DVD.

I love to watch Ken Davis.  He is a Christian man using comedy to proclaim the Gospel!  And He does such a great job!  I think many souls could be brought to Christ with the message in this dvd.  May Mr. Davis live long and continue the good work!
Very poignant and the typical Ken Davis humor
Ken Davis is a great teacher and comedian. Absolutely uplifting and powerful!
